{"tid":1555472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟有幾句野想同各位手足講 希望睇一睇","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T11:30:43.000Z","uid":209131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e00f73592d37ed0825d56e50eae9290825c12c95","tid":1555472,"uid":209131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3個月嘅社運 71真係做得最好嘅一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n但依家開始愈黎愈唔對路 見到地鐵就破壞 對準政權啊 破壞完又比位新聞入話示威者大肆破壞 破壞地鐵又冇意義 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得狗鐵會在意幾部機幾塊玻璃咩?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個香港人都睇連登 佢地唔知點解要搞地鐵 令佢地開始反感 依家民意好重要架 冇民意仲邊有人支持我地 係街邊仲邊有人會幫手出聲<br />\n<br />\n打狗個方面有件事想提你地 點解咁多人企係防暴前面食花生 依家啲狗望佢兩眼就過黎搞你 你又唔係要打 得個口罩做咩企咁前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗仔衝嘅時候人多一定有人跑慢 有眼你睇好多被捕者都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n陣線不嬲都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(前線&gt;支援/救人/遠攻&gt;和理非屌狗)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係要分化同指責 絕不割不分化 希望大家諗清楚啲 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好比仇恨沖昏頭腦</span></span> 抗爭唔係玩遊戲"},{"pid":"aa8dad30d3fbec32615ff46e8e4c4410bf587b8b","tid":1555472,"uid":209131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b460c896e0e6896b61e80aeb1022e118c4324d2c","tid":1555472,"uid":209131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"05158ec02bf246d94d68ef357169c90ae3ae7354","tid":1555472,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"「經歷2代殖民」依加嘅新屋嶺 = 舊時嘅摩星嶺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a21144467e12d45a3c9a63f78be0ae880dfed378","tid":1555472,"uid":209131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09